The paper deals with the protection of data and accounts against hackers, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning algorithms (cs.AI) and cluster analysis (cs.LG, cs.DS) to detect false usernames. Additionally, the paper discusses the application of these security systems in different areas, such as social opinion studies and protection of information in user accounts, which falls under the category of social and information sciences (cs.SI).
